====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# Words or a [[formula]] supposed to have [[magical]] powers.
#: ''He cast a '''spell''' to cure warts.''
# A magical effect induced by an incantation or formula.
#: ''under a '''spell'''''
# A [[splinter]], usually of [[wood]] ([[Lancashire]]/[[Yorkshire]]).
# A mild or momentary emotional outburst.
# {{context|informal|epilepsy}} A [[petit mal]]
# {{cricket}} An uninterrupted series of [[alternate]] [[over]]s bowled by a single [[bowler]].
# {{context|horseracing}} [[time off]] from competition

